Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:18.88,SeriesTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(334.133,309.733)\fad(150,270)}Brave{\fscx900} {\r}Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:24.55,SongOP,,0,0,0,,Over a million of them shine with a blue light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:31.23,SongOP,,0,0,0,,The shards of love have scattered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:38.23,SongOP,,0,0,0,,It's brewing in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:41.19,SongOP,,0,0,0,,A storm that you'll confront
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:44.74,SongOP,,0,0,0,,And because I believe in you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:49.66,SongOP,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:53.87,SongOP,,0,0,0,,GO WITH ME Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:57.29,SongOP,,0,0,0,,Courage and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:01:03.34,SongOP,,0,0,0,,That moment when we join our strength GATHER WAY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:06.89,SongOP,,0,0,0,,GO WITH ME Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:10.26,SongOP,,0,0,0,,I'd almost forgotten it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:18.61,SongOP,,0,0,0,,The fiery burning and important PASSIONATE feeling in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have gone horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,God Max and Ultra Raker got captured by Dino Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mr. Tokuda was also taken \Ninstead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, Dino Geist will havoc Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:18.82,EpisodeTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(326.4,326)}The True Treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous, Kouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tokuda got abducted instead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean that I can take \NKouta to a dangerous place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'll be of some use!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we must go save Mr. Tokuda quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And also God Max and Ultra Raker...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't do anything dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please open this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This couldn't be a prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way! Tokuda Osamu, 29 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I going to die here without \Neven doing filial piety...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are, \Nbut thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Who's this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dino Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't that brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please spare me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen him before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the assistant of that quack \Ndoctor that we once captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm meeting you all for the first time... Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember it clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you guys' fault that our \Nprevious base got destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dino Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy was the one who called that \NExkaiser bastard to our base!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that means that Exkaiser will \Ncome here even if it's not that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like he'll appear immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser will come?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For my sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I that much of a celebrity...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dino Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, if we put a trap here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear Mr. Tokuda's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's from this direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tokuda's voice has been inputted in my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine to be amused, but don't kill him yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll... I'll die already so please stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't die yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's come...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you torment a human\N who can't fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's the day when I'll settle things with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And today's also the last day when \Nyou'll be able to say that line!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Dino Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,King Loader!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Form Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Giant Fusion, Great Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come, Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This pond is a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lucky bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunder, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Double Fusion, Pteder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Double Fusion, Hormor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't dodge now, Great Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the end of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, Exkaiser will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,God Max! Ultra Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And now off with your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Kouta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tokuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that I was going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry to a safe place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:10:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought this camera with my\N efficiency bonus for times like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tokuda! It's dangerous to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to make this scoop of the \Ncentury my own! Just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tokuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Dino Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How impudent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the greatest shutter chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this, Dino Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we'll get you with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to kept you waiting, Great Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,God Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave these guys to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,God Max! Ultra Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've captured this brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be the last souvenir from this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,God Max! Ultra Raker! I leave the rest to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you escape, Dino Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw away your weapons if you don't \Nwant this kid to be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Is this kid that important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not only Kouta who's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All the lives that exist in this \Nuniverse are important!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that in order to protect \Nthis puny Earthling's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't care what happens to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how small it is, life is a treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's a life of a villain like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You say amusing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll steal your important life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Thunder Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:13:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino Twin Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on, Dino Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunder Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Thunder Inferno!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll arrest you under the laws of space!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Things won't be going your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We've entered the sun's gravity range!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is a treasure, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I can't let you have this life of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino Geist...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't done anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't do bad things anymore, so forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys were so clumsy that \Nwe ended up like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:16:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What a noisy bunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tokuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank god!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like our mission is finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! I managed to get a lot \Nof photos of this scoop...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's take a commemorative photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so big that you don't all \Nfit in the camera's frame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheese-...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tokuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's alright... My camera didn't break!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I think they'll be back soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've helped me in various ways until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask for the impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My next mission is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Parting is tough for me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're my important friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's so, then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been great if you could've played once with my little sisters and brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Drill Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid! A lot of things happened, but it was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We made some nice memories at Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:19:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinkansen trains were certainly\N interesting vehicles!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Raker! Green Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our farewell at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But this planet sure was a \Nplanet with a lot of treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! There were a lot of unusual treasures, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The greatest treasure for me was that\N I could meet Exkaiser and you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Be well, Kouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we... meet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't promise that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:20:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter where I am in the universe,\N I'm always watching over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like for you to remember that \NI'm always in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Send my regards to your sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz345.6\pos(174.4,284.4)}Dino Geist Is Finally Defeated
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz52.07\pos(480,127.6)}Peace Returns on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Peace Returns on Earth."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Tokuda! You sure did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just that skilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your first big scoop since \Nyou started as a reporter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a second helping!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tokuda, you're so easy to please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Soy boiled food is your reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't flatter me so much, Fuuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where is Kouta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You somewhat look like you've separated \Nfrom your important friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what kind of friend \Nyou've separated from...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But doesn't Kouta have papa and your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an important child for me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that your separated friend \Nwill come back one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then! Eat breakfast and cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, everyone will be worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan and Takumi-kun too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:21:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi-kun, thanks for giving me a lift!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:22:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan, weren't we going to \N go to school together?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta-kun, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go to school quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat breakfast and get energetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter where I am in the universe,\N I'm always watching over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like for you to remember that \NI'm always in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.02,0:22:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.34,0:22:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.19,0:22:56.20,SongED,,0,0,0,,Faraway wind carries your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:23:05.29,SongED,,0,0,0,,What could you discover from this excited feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.00,0:23:15.34,SongED,,0,0,0,,Dreams get bigger strongly and fast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.34,0:23:22.97,SongED,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to be who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:31.27,SongED,,0,0,0,,Embrace your enthusiastic heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:39.28,SongED,,0,0,0,,And try walking that path
